Package: mousedamper
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         mousedamper-common (= ${source:Version}),
         libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.50),
         libevdev2
Description: Mouse damper to prevent accidental clicks
 Mouse Damper is a utility that helps prevent accidental clicks caused by
 hand tremors or unsteady mouse movements by temporarily freezing the mouse
 pointer during button presses.
 .
 This package contains the mousedamper daemon binary.

Package: mousedamper-common
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3,
         python3-gi,
         gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
         gir1.2-xapp-1.0,
         gir1.2-glib-2.0,
         gir1.2-gio-2.0
Description: Mouse damper to prevent accidental clicks
 Mouse Damper is a utility that helps prevent accidental clicks caused by
 hand tremors or unsteady mouse movements by temporarily freezing the mouse
 pointer during button presses.
 .
 This package contains scripts, icons and data files for mousedamper.

Package: mousedamper-dbg
Section: debug
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: mousedamper (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mouse damper to prevent accidental clicks (debug symbols)
 Mouse Damper is a utility that helps prevent accidental clicks caused by
 hand tremors or unsteady mouse movements by temporarily freezing the mouse
 pointer during button presses.
 .
 This package contains the debug symbols for mousedamper.
